If a Mage passes within a radius of 3 of a roaming demon, the roamer will start following the mage. 
Every time a mage takes a step with a demon following it, it looses an additional one mana point. Every time the roamer takes a step, it loses 0.25 health.
If a mage manages to escape a roamer, by killing it (the roamer runs out of health), the mage will gain two experience points and five gold.